{"word":"G82 - ἄδηλος - ádēlos - ad'-ay-los - Appear not","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄδηλος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ádēlos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad'-ay-los</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appear not</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"காணாமல், தெரியாதிருக்கிற, விளங்காத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not manifest indistinct, uncertain, obscure"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1212 - δῆλος - dēlos - day'-los/1212\">G1212</a>; <i>hidden</i>, figuratively <i>indistinct:</i> - appear not, uncertain.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}